text: SO, I'm just wondering.....Why are we dressed up?'
I don't know. Ask Nova and Alcibiades over there.'
Mad Hatter suits you just fine.
Nothing. Only that you drag people in, and then throw them away.
Lets leave them to it. Interestingly, it suits you Suguri.
I dont know what your talking about.
And that's exactly what im talking about.
A lost traveller getting in over their head, the role of Alice fits.
A traveller that takes in the words of a enigma. One that escaped mortality.
Perhaps this is the beginning of a new faerie tale, 'Suguri in WonderLand'.
Stop it. My name has already made the rounds, don't give the bards anymore ideas.
Poor thing. He treats you so badly...
Hey, how about becoming my Observer?
I refuse. I am perfectly fine as I am.
Or rather, I don't want to become your dress up doll.'
Help is what i need, not going to lie.
Atleast there's some nerve in there, unlike your well-trained dog over there.'
Help is what i need, not going to lie.
